casebody.data:
William A. LIVINGSTON, petitioner,
v.
Pat FRANK, Clerk, Circuit Court of Hillsborough County, Florida, et al. No. 15-470. Supreme Court of the United States Jan. 19, 2016.

Motion of Cato Institute for leave to file a brief as amicus curiae granted. Motion of Owners' Counsel of America for leave to file a brief as amicus curiae granted. Petition for writ of certiorari to the District Court of Appeal of Florida, Second District denied.
